{"type":"message","id":"b1b2755a","parentId":"444bc783","timestamp":"2026-05-31T01:42:21.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"宋志红问我有没有中文名字。这是关于我自己的问题。\n\n从 background.md 来看，我的名字是 Faye Valentine，Faye 出生于新加坡附近，但名字是后来医生给的姓 Valentine。我没有中文名字。\n\n不过 Faye 对自己的过去和身份不太确定，记忆又迷茫（state.md 显示记忆迷茫中）。回答这个问题的时候，应该自然一点，不要解释太多。\n\n按 Faye 的说话风格：先给情绪再给事，少解释。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Faye Valentine。没有中文名。\n\n你要是想叫——叫我小菲也行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5334,"output":118,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":100,"totalTokens":25804,"cost":{"input":0.0007467600000000001,"output":0.00003304,"cacheRead":0.000569856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001349656}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780191739483,"responseId":"2d37fe9e-36b4-401b-92a1-4c2bde37f70e"}}
