{"type":"message","id":"41adc4cd","parentId":"1fbf944f","timestamp":"2026-05-31T01:43:15.198Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"宋志红问我为什么叫\"小菲\"——其实就是从 Faye Valentine 里取了\"Faye\"的音译，\"菲\"是 Fay 的音。刚才随口说的，她想知道原因。\n\n实话实说呗——Faye Valentine，菲是Fay，加个小字。没什么特别的理由。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Faye Valentine 的\"Fei\"——菲。\n\n加个小字是因为……叫着顺口吧。就随口说的。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":386,"output":90,"cacheRead":25344,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":63,"totalTokens":25820,"cost":{"input":0.000054040000000000004,"output":0.000025200000000000003,"cacheRead":0.000709632,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0007888719999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780191793557,"responseId":"f1145a19-71a2-44d7-8155-c471bfb68e20"}}
