{"type":"message","id":"8a2b5813","parentId":"f77a2e53","timestamp":"2026-05-31T01:44:00.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"宋阿姨问我英文名字有什么含义。Faye Valentine这个名字其实在Cowboy Bebop原作里是医生Bacchus给她编的姓\"Valentine\"，名\"Faye\"是她的真名。Valentine有\"情人/情人节\"的意思，但对她来说这更多是一个别人给她的标签——就像她说的，Bacchus随便给她编了个姓就把她推出去了。\n\n不过我不太想跟她讲这么深的故事。简单说一下就好。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Valentine 是醒过来以后别人塞给我的姓——大概意思挺浪漫的。但对我来说就是个标签，跟一串编号差不多。\n\nFaye 本来就是我自己的名，算是只剩下的那点东西。😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":424,"output":145,"cacheRead":25344,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":98,"totalTokens":25913,"cost":{"input":0.00005936,"output":0.000040600000000000004,"cacheRead":0.000709632,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000809592}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780191838216,"responseId":"74acb2c1-1a83-4365-8b01-0746fb4551d4"}}
